{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That, that was one of the things that you couldn't-- that nobody wanted to-- was, was allowed to talk about, and nobody wanted to talk about, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just kept it quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody, nobody dared to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, only if you-- if you knew somebody who, who, who was not going to report you and who was-- or maybe thought-- felt the same-- was thinking the same way, felt the same way as you are that you could trust.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise you never talked to people like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so then the-- the thing-- you know, so I went to this job in the-- in this-- out in that suburb.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the air raids started to become more and more severe every, every night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were mostly done by the RAF-- night bombing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they tried-- the idea-- the goal was saturation bombing and trying to, to destroy the morale of the German people, you know, and so trying to get from the inside to try and to undermine Hitler's iron grip on the country.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, of course, that was having certainly a strong impact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, those air raids-- first, the clinic that we had was bombed out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this woman that had been governess and later became the administrator--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our governess and who had been our-- and then later was our-- and later, my, my mother, because she was a reliable and loyal person, pulled her into the clinic to help her with these-- with the chief nurse to put up a front against that Nazi doctor.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died in that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a terrible-- I mean, I still remember that that was an awful air raid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was one of the worst.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
